title: Müjgan
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Mediterranean, European, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An arty cafe in lively university neighborhood of Yuzuncu Yil. Food, paintings and sometimes live music. Walking distance to ODTU and Cankaya University. Has vegan-vegetarian options such as Italian style pasta, vegan burger varieties, falafel, vegan pastry, and occasionally vegetable soup. Staff usually consists of university students so they can speak English. Though not labeled every veg option has either vegan or sebze (vegetable) word in its name.
streetAddress: 100. Yıl İşçi Blokları Mahallesi 1533. Sokak 2/24 Çankaya
